Issue
├── id (UUID)
├── organization_id (FK)
├── title
├── description
├── priority (critical, high, medium, low)
├── status (open, in_progress, pending_approval, resolved, closed)
├── assignee_id (FK - User)
├── reporter_id (FK - User)
├── risk_id (FK - Risk, optional)
├── root_cause
├── remediation_plan
├── due_date
├── resolved_at
├── resolution_notes
├── tags (array)
├── created_at
└── updated_at